rows.label: qst102104_msg0003
rows.name: How did the mission go for you?

rows.label: qst102104_msg0004
rows.name:
Are you used to the
mercenary corps yet?

rows.label: qst102104_msg0101
rows.name:
I defeated my three targets right
away and was the first one here, mo.

rows.label: qst102104_msg0103
rows.name:
Everyone else is late, mo. This is
a group activity, so I wish they'd
be a little more punctual, mo.

rows.label: qst102104_msg0202
rows.name:
I still haven't quite figured
out who and what is where
in this village, mo.

rows.label: qst102104_msg0203
rows.name:
There are too many steps for Nopon
legs, so it's hard to get around.
I can't get used to it, mo.
